  "instructions": [
    "Heat a skillet over medium-high heat and add a drizzle of olive oil.",
    "Add the beef to the skillet and cook until browned, about 5-7 minutes on each side.",
    "Remove the beef from the skillet and set aside. Add the onion and garlic to the skillet, sautéing for 2-3 minutes until softened.",
    "Add cilantro, lime juice, hot sauce, salt, and pepper to the skillet. Stir well to combine.",
    "Return the cooked beef to the skillet with the mixture. Stir everything together until all ingredients are evenly coated.",
    "Serve hot."
  ],
